data.text:
Finishing the Bay Bridge constructionIt is said that construction on the San Francisco Bay Bridge will be completed in 2013. That said... (a humorous take)However, the end of the world is scheduled to be taking place December 21, 2012. With that said, one can surmise that the Bay Bridge will never be completed. At least not in this lifetime.

The world won't end in 12/21/12. Its nonsense. The Mayans thought the world is going to end what the hell
